<title>Ƴan Tumaki Ne Mu a Tsakiyar Kerketai LW282</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Ƴan tumaki ne mu a tsakiyar kerketai,
 Amma &quot;Haka na aike ku,&quot; Ubangiji ya  e.

[V2]
 2) Jawabinsa kaɗai kayan yaƙinmu ne.
 In ji shi, &quot;Mulkin Allah ne ya zo kusa da ku.&quot;

[V3]
 3) Ko kisanmu sā yi, ko wuya za mu sha,
 An kashe Ubangijinmu, balle iyalinsa.

[V4]
 4) Mu ɗauki giciyensa, bayansa za mu bi,
 Domin a ranar zuwansa, mu karƃi yabonsa.</lyrics>
</song>